<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Productivity Hub Overview</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --surface: rgba(37, 28, 23, 0.92);
        --surface-soft: rgba(255, 244, 232, 0.05);
        --text: #f4ede3;
        --muted: #c7b7a2;
        --line: rgba(233, 220, 198, 0.12);
        --oak: #6c4c34;
        --oak-light: #8b6647;
        --forest: #3a4a32;
        --navy: #2a3444;
        --gold: #b08a4b;
        --accent: #7b2d2f;
        --shadow: 0 28px 72px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.32);
        --radius-xl: 32px;
        --radius-lg: 24px;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 12% 18%, rgba(0, 255, 170, 0.16), transparent 18%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 88% 20%, rgba(0, 170, 255, 0.18), transparent 20%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 76% 78%, rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.14), transparent 18%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 20% 82%, rgba(255, 184, 0, 0.12), transparent 16%),
          linear-gradient(160deg, #050816 0%, #0a1020 42%, #120b1f 100%);
      }

      .page {
        width: min(1200px, calc(100% - 32px));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 28px 0 56px;
      }

      .hero,
      .panel,
      .feature-card,
      .metric-card,
      .page-card {
        background:
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02), transparent),
          var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .hero {
        border-radius: 40px;
        padding: 42px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 24px;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        font-size: 0.74rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--gold);
      }

      h1,
      h2,
      h3 {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5.6rem);
        line-height: 0.94;
        max-width: 11ch;
      }

      .hero-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
        gap: 20px;
        align-items: start;
      }

      .hero-copy p:last-child,
      .panel p,
      .feature-card p,
      .metric-card p,
      .page-card p,
      li {
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .pill {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 11px 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .pill.primary {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--forest), #4d6143);
        color: #fff8f1;
      }

      .pill.hero-pill {
        padding: 16px 24px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        box-shadow: 0 16px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }

      .pill.secondary {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        color: var(--text);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .showcase {
        border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
        padding: 22px;
      }

      .showcase-screen {
        border-radius: 24px;
        background: rgba(7, 8, 10, 0.34);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        padding: 18px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .showcase-pages,
      .showcase-row,
      .showcase-bars,
      .showcase-metrics,
      .showcase-body {
        display: grid;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .showcase-pages {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(5, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .showcase-row {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .showcase-bars {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(7, minmax(0, 1fr));
        align-items: end;
        min-height: 180px;
      }

      .showcase-metrics {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .showcase-card,
      .showcase-stat,
      .showcase-page {
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: var(--surface-soft);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        padding: 12px;
      }

      .mini-label {
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }

      .mini-title {
        font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #fff7eb;
      }

      .mini-copy {
        font-size: 0.84rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.45;
        margin-top: 6px;
      }

      .mini-number {
        font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: #fff1d8;
      }

      .mini-page-pill {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 100%;
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--muted);
        border: 0;
        background: transparent;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .mini-page-pill.active {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), #3a4758);
        color: #fff7eb;
      }

      .log-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 8px;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }

      .log-item {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 12px;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .mini-grade-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 12px;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-top: 8px;
      }

      .mini-grade-pill {
        padding: 6px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(123, 45, 47, 0.18);
        color: #ffd8d4;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .showcase-bar {
        border-radius: 14px 14px 8px 8px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--oak-light), var(--oak));
      }

      .showcase-bar:nth-child(2n) {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #485c40, var(--forest));
      }

      .showcase-bar:nth-child(3n) {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #3c4657, var(--navy));
      }

      .is-hidden {
        display: none;
      }

      .section {
        margin-top: 22px;
      }

      .panel {
        border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
        padding: 28px;
      }

      .grid-3 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .grid-2 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .feature-card,
      .metric-card,
      .page-card {
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        padding: 22px;
      }

      .metric-number {
        font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
        font-size: 2.4rem;
        color: #fff4df;
      }

      .page-card ul,
      .panel ul {
        margin: 14px 0 0;
        padding-left: 18px;
      }

      .footnote {
        margin-top: 24px;
        padding: 18px 22px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      @media (max-width: 960px) {
        .hero-grid,
        .grid-3,
        .grid-2 {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .showcase-row,
        .showcase-pages,
        .showcase-metrics {
          grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .page {
          width: min(100% - 20px, 100%);
          padding: 18px 0 38px;
        }

        .hero,
        .panel,
        .feature-card,
        .metric-card,
        .page-card {
          border-radius: 24px;
        }

        .hero {
          padding: 24px;
        }

        .showcase-pages,
        .showcase-metrics,
        .showcase-row {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="page">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div class="hero-copy">
            <p class="eyebrow">Project Overview</p>
            <h1>Productivity Hub</h1>
            <p>
              Productivity Hub is a personal academic command center designed to help students track study habits,
              class performance, and time investment in one place.
            </p>
            <p>
              It combines session logging, class-grade tracking, visual analytics, exam-prep comparisons, and a
              central home dashboard into one polished academic system.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
              <span class="pill primary hero-pill">Built for students, designed for success</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <aside class="showcase">
            <p class="eyebrow">Interactive Snapshot</p>
            <div class="showcase-screen">
              <div class="showcase-pages">
                <div class="showcase-page"><button class="mini-page-pill active" data-demo-tab="home">Home</button></div>
                <div class="showcase-page"><button class="mini-page-pill" data-demo-tab="sessions">Sessions</button></div>
                <div class="showcase-page"><button class="mini-page-pill" data-demo-tab="classes">Classes</button></div>
                <div class="showcase-page"><button class="mini-page-pill" data-demo-tab="charts">Charts</button></div>
                <div class="showcase-page"><button class="mini-page-pill" data-demo-tab="stats">Stats</button></div>
              </div>

              <div class="showcase-body" data-demo-panel="home">
                <div class="showcase-row">
                  <div class="showcase-card">
                    <div class="mini-label">Classes</div>
                    <div class="mini-title">Biology 201</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Weighted GPA: 3.70</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-card">
                    <div class="mini-label">Current Timer</div>
                    <div class="mini-number">01:24:12</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Current study block</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-card">
                    <div class="mini-label">Semester GPA</div>
                    <div class="mini-number">3.58</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Across 4 classes</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="showcase-metrics">
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Study Logs</div>
                    <div class="log-list">
                      <div class="log-item"><span>Biology - Midterm Review</span><span>90 min</span></div>
                      <div class="log-item"><span>Psychology - Quiz Prep</span><span>45 min</span></div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Grades</div>
                    <div class="mini-grade-row"><span>Exam 1</span><span class="mini-grade-pill">92%</span></div>
                    <div class="mini-grade-row"><span>Quiz 2</span><span class="mini-grade-pill">87%</span></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Stats</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Top subject: Biology</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Study share: 34%</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Avg session: 72 min</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="showcase-body is-hidden" data-demo-panel="sessions">
                <div class="showcase-row">
                  <div class="showcase-card">
                    <div class="mini-label">Latest Log</div>
                    <div class="mini-title">Biology</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Midterm Review • 90 min • Study</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-card">
                    <div class="mini-label">Sorting</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Newest First / Class A-Z</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-card">
                    <div class="mini-label">Assignment Link</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Tie a study block to an exam, quiz, or project while logging it.</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="showcase-metrics">
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Form Inputs</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Subject</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Assignment</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Duration</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Saved Logs</div>
                    <div class="log-list">
                      <div class="log-item"><span>Calc Quiz 3</span><span>60 min</span></div>
                      <div class="log-item"><span>Psych Notes</span><span>45 min</span></div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Editing</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Update old sessions</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Attach assignment outcomes</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="showcase-body is-hidden" data-demo-panel="classes">
                <div class="showcase-row">
                  <div class="showcase-card">
                    <div class="mini-label">Biology 201</div>
                    <div class="mini-number">3.70</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Class GPA</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-card">
                    <div class="mini-label">Semester GPA</div>
                    <div class="mini-number">3.58</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Across graded classes</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-card">
                    <div class="mini-label">Weight Entered</div>
                    <div class="mini-number">65%</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Assignments entered so far</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="showcase-metrics">
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Assignments</div>
                    <div class="mini-grade-row"><span>Exam 1</span><span class="mini-grade-pill">92%</span></div>
                    <div class="mini-grade-row"><span>Quiz 2</span><span class="mini-grade-pill">87%</span></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Weights</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Exam 1 • 25%</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Quiz 2 • 10%</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Detail View</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Open a class</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Edit assignments</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Track class GPA</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="showcase-body is-hidden" data-demo-panel="charts">
                <div class="showcase-bars">
                  <div class="showcase-bar" style="height: 44%;"></div>
                  <div class="showcase-bar" style="height: 73%;"></div>
                  <div class="showcase-bar" style="height: 58%;"></div>
                  <div class="showcase-bar" style="height: 84%;"></div>
                  <div class="showcase-bar" style="height: 62%;"></div>
                  <div class="showcase-bar" style="height: 38%;"></div>
                  <div class="showcase-bar" style="height: 69%;"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="showcase-metrics">
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Filters</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Class</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Week range</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Current week</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Drill Down</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Open a week</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">See all 7 days</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Insight</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Weekly comparison</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Per-class distribution</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="showcase-body is-hidden" data-demo-panel="stats">
                <div class="showcase-row">
                  <div class="showcase-card">
                    <div class="mini-label">Top Subject</div>
                    <div class="mini-title">Biology</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">34% of total study time</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-card">
                    <div class="mini-label">Average Session</div>
                    <div class="mini-number">72m</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Typical study block</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-card">
                    <div class="mini-label">Most Active Day</div>
                    <div class="mini-title">Tuesday</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">3 hr 10 min total</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="showcase-metrics">
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Prep Comparison</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Exam 1 • 92%</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">5 hr 40 min studied</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Subject Share</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Biology • 34%</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Psychology • 22%</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="showcase-stat">
                    <div class="mini-label">Critical Stats</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Focus balance</div>
                    <div class="mini-copy">Time per subject</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Core Value</p>
        <h2>What The Website Is Meant To Do</h2>
        <p>
          Productivity Hub gives students a single place to understand how they spend time, how that connects to grades,
          and where to focus next. Instead of juggling separate notes, trackers, and planners, the project is meant to
          centralize all of that into one polished interface.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section grid-3">
        <article class="metric-card">
          <p class="eyebrow">Sessions</p>
          <div class="metric-number">Track</div>
          <p>Log study sessions by class, assignment, date, duration, category, and notes.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="metric-card">
          <p class="eyebrow">Classes</p>
          <div class="metric-number">Calculate</div>
          <p>Store weighted class grades and keep a running GPA for each course and the semester.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="metric-card">
          <p class="eyebrow">Stats</p>
          <div class="metric-number">Compare</div>
          <p>See how preparation time connects to exam and assignment outcomes over time.</p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="section panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Pages</p>
        <h2>What People Can Explore</h2>
        <div class="grid-2 section">
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>Home</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Intro dashboard for the product</li>
              <li>Built-in study timer</li>
              <li>Quick summary of activity</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>Sessions</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Log and edit study sessions</li>
              <li>Sort sessions by class</li>
              <li>Attach assignments and outcomes to study logs</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>Classes</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Open individual classes</li>
              <li>Enter weighted grades for assignments, quizzes, and exams</li>
              <li>See class GPA and semester GPA</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>Charts</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Compare study time week to week</li>
              <li>Break selected weeks into daily views</li>
              <li>Understand how time is distributed across subjects</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>Stats</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Subject percentages and total study time</li>
              <li>Most active day, average session, and focus balance</li>
              <li>Grade vs study-time comparison</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>Calendar Placeholder</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Reserved for future planning and schedule integrations</li>
              <li>Future smart study planning potential</li>
              <li>Designed to grow with the project</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section grid-2">
        <article class="feature-card">
          <p class="eyebrow">Why It Stands Out</p>
          <h3>It Connects Effort To Results</h3>
          <p>
            The project is not just a timer or a gradebook. It is designed to show whether the way a student studies is
            actually translating into better academic performance.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="feature-card">
          <p class="eyebrow">Why It Is Practical</p>
          <h3>It Is Ready To Demonstrate</h3>
          <p>
            The current version already shows how a student can track sessions, class performance, and study analytics
            inside one connected product experience.
          </p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <div class="footnote">
        This page is a standalone presentation page only. It is separate from the actual app and does not change the
        working website itself.
      </div>
    </main>
    <script>
      const buttons = document.querySelectorAll("[data-demo-tab]");
      const panels = document.querySelectorAll("[data-demo-panel]");

      buttons.forEach((button) => {
        button.addEventListener("click", () => {
          const nextTab = button.getAttribute("data-demo-tab");

          buttons.forEach((item) => {
            item.classList.toggle("active", item === button);
          });

          panels.forEach((panel) => {
            panel.classList.toggle("is-hidden", panel.getAttribute("data-demo-panel") !== nextTab);
          });
        });
      });
    </script>
  </body>
  </html>
